    • MenuItem

      public MenuItem(String name, String description, double price, FoodCategory foodType)
      Create a new MenuItem according to the name of menu item, menu item desciption, menu item price, menu item food category
      Parameters:
      name - This is the name of the menu Item
      description - This is description of the menu item
      price - This is the price ie. the unit cost of a menu item
      foodType - This is an enumeration. Ir refers to the food category of a menu item. It can only be 1 of the 3 food categories (1) MAIN COURSE, 2) DRINKS, 3) DESSERT
